      "explanation": {
        "title": "Full supply chain transparency",
        "p1": "HalalChain creates a digital thread connecting every entity in your supply chain. Each product batch receives a unique identifier that follows it from raw materials to the end consumer.",
        "p2": "Suppliers are onboarded with verified halal certifications. Products are logged with complete ingredient lists and processing methods. Certifications are attached digitally and monitored for expiry.",
        "p3": "Warehouse operators scan incoming and outgoing shipments, updating inventory in real-time. When products ship, customers receive tracking information and can verify authenticity by scanning the QR code on the packaging."
      }
